MODE
GRAB 300
MARK L
COPY F X
REPL WALKER
TEST EOF
TJMP HALT
JUMP L

MARK WALKER
LINK 800
MARK WALK
LINK 800
SUBI X 100 X
TEST X < 100
FJMP WALK
ADDI 200 X X
GRAB X
REPL COPIER
MARK RELAY
COPY F M
TEST EOF
FJMP RELAY
COPY -9999 M
JUMP HALT

MARK COPIER
MAKE
MARK COPY
COPY M X
TEST X = -9999
TJMP HOME
COPY X F
JUMP COPY
MARK HOME
@REP 10
LINK -1
@END
MARK HALT
HALT
